---
const { title, description } = Astro.props;
---

<footer id="footer" class="panel">
  <div class="inner split">
    <div>
      <section>
        <h2>{title}</h2>
        <h3>摄影师介绍</h3>
        <p>嗨，我是Irande，一个永远在路上的故事收集者。我的相机里，不只装得下山河湖海的壮阔，也装得下市井街头的温柔。关注我，带你一起，把远方变成日常。</p>
        <h3>拍摄设备</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>索尼 A6000</li>
          <li>OPPO Find X7 Ultra</li>
          <li>iPhone15Pro</li>
          <li>适马 16mm F1.4 DC 镜头</li>
          <li>小痰盂 18-50 镜头</li>
        </ul>
        <h3>投稿和联系方式</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>📧 邮箱：beilanzhisen@163.com</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="social-links">
          <a href="https://instagram.com/irande">Instagram</a> | 
          <a href="https://weibo.com/irande">微博</a> | 
          <a href="https://xiaohongshu.com/irande">小红书</a> | 
          <a href="https://bilibili.com/irande">B站</a>
        </div>
          <div class="copyright-footer">
    <div class="copyright-container">
      <p class="copyright-text">
        <span class="copyright-symbol">©</span>
        <span class="copyright-year">2025</span>
        <span class="copyright-name">Irande Photography</span>
        <span class="separator">|</span>
        <span class="copyright-info">所有作品均为原创拍摄</span>
      </p>
    </div>
      </section>
    </div>
    <div>
      <section>
        <h2>联系我们</h2>
        <form method="post" action="#">
          <div class="fields">
            <div class="field half">
              <input type="text" name="name" id="name" placeholder="姓名" />
            </div>
            <div class="field half">
              <input type="text" name="email" id="email" placeholder="邮箱" />
            </div>
            <div class="field">
              <textarea
                name="message"
                id="message"
                rows="4"
                placeholder="留言内容"></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
          <ul class="actions">
            <li><input type="submit" value="发送" class="primary" /></li>
            <li><input type="reset" value="重置" /></li>
          </ul>
        </form>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
</footer>